_sText:
4th map. This map I decided to try something different by doing a night themed map. I tried to add as much lighting as I could without taking the night time element away from it all. There are a couple of brands I stuck in. As advertisement for our gaming community. We are still taking people on if your interested. And more importantly, we mix. :)

Sorry if you don't like the fog in the map. I did fade it as much as possible without removing the " late night mist " effect from it. As you get from water irl. 

Enjoy :)
